{
  "stem": "13623.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We're coming into the block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The beds over there is what you see in a-- in a warehouse, like big, wide shelves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I would say six or eight people were sleeping on one of those shelves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was-- I don't remember if it was two or three stories high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We are in that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We are assigned this block.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Everybody is ordered to go outside, line up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had to line up five-- five abreast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had to all line up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were standing there for a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Finally, an SS officer came, and he starts counting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He goes 5, 10, 15-- we were five abreast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He counted everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were allowed to go back into the barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We are being given a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The-- a loaf of bread was as big, approximately, as a brick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that loaf of bread was for three people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So each three people would have to-- we would cut that loaf of bread as accurate as possible, so nobody got a bigger piece than the next guy or a smaller piece than the next guy.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that was our food for the day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We're-- we're let out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we're walking around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we're seeing other people that came from other ghettos that were in the same clothing that we were in, in these striped prisoner clothes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- some of us still don't believe, or don't want to believe after talking to the older prisoners that were there, that our mothers and our rest of our families are not alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It's only the following day.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
